item.title: Usage HTB Walkthrough
item.description: The Usage HTB machine is a madium difficulty level HackTheBox Machine. The main techniques and tools used to crack this machine are: - Blind SQL injection with SQLmap - Burpsuite - Hash cracking with JohnTheRipper - 7z Wildcard Spare exploitation Reconnaissance Link to heading We start a broad Nmap scan by executing the following command: sudo nmap -sS -T5 -vvv -p- 10.10.11.18 -Pn -oG nmap_inicial Where the arguments mean:
